These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, jazz, trance
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, puzzles, magic-tricks, cooking
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, grey, azure, ivory
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, dannemann, pall-mall, alhambra
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
 2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 3. the fan of blues is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who likes ivory is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 5. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##5
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5
 7. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 9. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
10. the person who likes ivory is somewhere between the prince-smoker and the fan of blues##7
11. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
13. the alhambra-smoker is the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | country | jazz    | blues   |
| Hobby   | skydiving | magic-tricks | puzzles | cooking |
| Color           | grey       | azure   | ivory  | apricot     |
| Cigar     | prince      | pall-mall   | alhambra    | dannemann    |

