.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, singing, photography, dancing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, thriller, time-travel
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, blend, siglo, cain
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, milk, lemonade
 1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 2. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5
 3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
 4. the person drinking milk is the davidoff-smoker##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
 6. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere between the person drinking water and the davidoff-smoker##7
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
10. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
11. the blend-smoker is the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby          | puzzles   | photography       | dancing    | singing      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | time-travel | crime         | thriller   |
| Cigar   | cain   | davidoff  | blend       | siglo |
| Beverage         | 7up      | milk  | lemonade | water |

