 7. the person who likes blood-red is not the blend-smoker##6
 8. the havana-smoker is not the person who likes lilac##6
 9. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
10. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
11. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
12. the modern house is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
