 6. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 8. the fan of punk is somewhere between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 9. the fan of punk is the person who growsrose##1
10. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
11. the fan of rock is not the person who growsrose##6

.:: Answer ::.
