 7. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
 8. the tower house is the fan of reggae##1
 9. the fan of soul is somewhere between the fan of reggae and the fan of classical##7
10. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan of reggae##5
11. the turkish is the tower house##1
12. the palace house is somewhere between the tower house and the person who growsballoon-flower##7
13. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the brazilian##3

.:: Answer ::.
