 4. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
 7. the nurse is somewhere between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching mystery movies##7
 8. the journalist is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
10. the doctor is the owner of the snake##1
11. the person playing poker is between the person playing chess and the journalist##2
12. the scientist is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
