 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the tower house##3
 4. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
 5. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the colonial house##5
 6. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
 7. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5
 8. the futuristic house is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 9. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the person eating tomato##7
10. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
11. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
12. the futuristic house is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
13. the person watching documentary movies is not the victorian house##6
14. the person watching epic movies is not the person eating onion##6
15. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the tower house and the person eating grapes##7

