.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, january, april, february
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, mystery, scientific
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, designer, scientist, dancer
4 different games are played: backgammon, go, scrabble, mah-jongg
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the firefighter is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
 4. the scientist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
 6. the person playing go is on the left or right of the designer##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the person playing backgammon and the person playing go##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is not the person playing backgammon##6
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
10. the person watching action movies is on the left of the scientist##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Birthday         | may      | january   | february   | april       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action    | disaster | mystery       |
| Job   | firefighter  | designer | scientist   | dancer     |
| Game         | backgammon   | mah-jongg    | go   | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, mirinda, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, designer, musician, teacher
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ebony, ivory, lavender
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, game, fonseca, tiparillo
 1. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
 3. the person who likes lavender is between the tiparillo-smoker and the fonseca-smoker##2
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the photographer##1
 5. the designer is not the game-smoker##6
 6. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the musician##5
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the teacher##7
 8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the fonseca-smoker##5
 9. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ebony##5
10. the designer is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is the musician##1
12. the musician is not the fonseca-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk   | tea     | mirinda   | iced-tea |
| Job       | teacher   | photographer | designer | musician    |
| Color      | ivory | lavender | fuchsia   | ebony  |
| Cigar        | tiparillo | dannemann     | fonseca   | game |

