.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, western, fantasy, disaster
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, fonseca, davidoff, vegafina
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, designer, police-officer, writer
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, australian, italian, nigerian
 1. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5
 2. the polish is between the davidoff-smoker and the architect##2
 3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
 5. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the australian is not the police-officer##6
 7. the police-officer is somewhere between the vegafina-smoker and the baccarat-smoker##7
 8. the polish is not the baccarat-smoker##6
 9. the writer is not the vegafina-smoker##6
10. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the polish##3
11. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the nigerian##1
12. the davidoff-smoker is not the person watching western movies##6
13. the police-officer is on the left of the writer##1
14. the architect is on the left or right of the polish##3
15. the designer is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Movie-Genre      | western      | time-travel        | disaster          | fantasy    |
| Cigar         | vegafina | fonseca    | davidoff          | baccarat |
| Job           | architect  | designer   | police-officer | writer      |
| Nationality   | nigerian       | polish | italian          | australian        |

