.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, billiard, backgammon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, disco, gospel, punk
City: rome, san-francisco, marseilles, london
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 2. the fan of gospel is the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is the person traveling to london##1
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing monopoly##2
 5. the fan of house is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
 6. the person traveling to rome is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the person playing canasta##7
 7. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the fan of disco##5
 8. the person traveling to rome is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
12. the fan of house is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Game   | backgammon      | billiard     | monopoly   | canasta    |
| Music-Genre     | punk | gospel   | disco | house |
| City     | london        | marseilles     | rome  | san-francisco      |
| Sport   | rowing       | water-polo | cricket   | skiing    |

 